networkx does not seem to preserve the order of the edges, so they
become uncorrelated with the edge color from the rates.  Maybe we need
a weighted graph:

https://networkx.github.io/documentation/networkx-1.9/examples/drawing/weighted_graph.html

https://networkx.github.io/documentation/networkx-1.10/reference/generated/networkx.DiGraph.add_weighted_edges_from.html


this seems promising:

http://stackoverflow.com/questions/22967086/colouring-edges-by-weight-in-networkx
